                  As a chef, I value my time at  <span class="dollarInput">£<input name="dollar" type="text" value="12">/hr</span>. My kitchen has <span class="chefInput"><input name="chef" type="text" value="3"> chefs</span> and we each spend <input type="text" name="time" value="15"> minutes a day on due dilligence.
                </p>
                <p>
                  This means I'll have an extra <strong class="totalTime">153 hours</strong> or <strong class="totalDollar">£1,836</strong> per year.
                </p>
